snippet.title: Fate/stay night Visual Novel (PC, 2004) - Opening 1
snippet.description:
First opening video of the visual novel "Fate/stay night" from the Japanese developer Type-Moon.
This opening was shown in the original PC version the game, released in 2004.

Developer's website: http://typemoon.com/ (Japanese)
